    <text type="letter">
        <body>


            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="loc.01965.001_large.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">N. Cambridge, Mass.</name>
                    <date when="1867-01-01">Jan. 1, 1867.</date>
                </dateline>
                <salute>Happy New Year, my dear friend!&#8212;</salute>
            </opener>

            <p>And here is a lot of luck for your new vol. of "Leaves."</p>

            <p>How are you, these days?</p>
            <p>I have a delightful letter from W.D. O'C.<!-- <ptr target="n0452"/> --> yesterday. Thank him
                for me.</p>

            <closer>
                <salute>Ever Yours</salute>
                <signed>J.T.Trowbridge<!-- <ptr target="n0651"/> --></signed>&gt;</closer>
            <postscript>
                <p>Walt Whitman.</p>
            </postscript>
        </body>
